1. Introduction
1.1 This Privacy Policy applies to each of the Companies entering in the Borzo Group Companies operating under the name "Borzo".
1.2 This Privacy Policy explains how the Companies collect, hold, process, transfer and use the Personal Information received from the Visitors or provided by the Users when using the Software.
1.3 This Privacy Policy applies to Personal Information of:
a. Visitors;
b. Users.
1.4 This Privacy Policy applies to wherever the Visitor is and is a master global Privacy Policy for the Borzo Group Companies. If the Visitor is accessing, operating, or using the Software in the following countries (the "Countries"), the Visitor must also read and acknowledge the Applicable PP that applies to the Visitor as follows:
Country Applicable - PP
Brazil -
https://borzodelivery.com/br/privacy-policy
India -
https://borzodelivery.com/in/privacy-policy
