(iii)
“Borzo Services"
mean Borzo India on-demand lead generation and related services that enable the Client to seek and receive on-demand requests for Courier Services from the Courier; such Borzo Services include access to Borzo App/Site and Borzo's software, payment services, and related support services systems, as may be updated or modified from time to time.
